BOILER SAFETY PROCEDURE

Department: Utilities

Machine: Steam Boiler

Author: Safety Officer

---------------------------------------------------

Routine Inspection

1. Check pressure gauge.
2. Verify water level.
3. Test safety valve.
4. Inspect steam leaks.

Safety Checklist

✔ Wear helmet
✔ Safety gloves
✔ Heat-resistant shoes
✔ Eye protection

Emergency Shutdown

1. Turn OFF fuel supply.
2. Activate emergency stop.
3. Open pressure relief valve.
4. Inform supervisor immediately.

Required Tools

Pressure Gauge
Flashlight
Thermal Camera

Estimated Inspection Time

15 Minutes